rtant wealth management hub where most of our product investment strategy and research solutions specialists teams as well as support functions for our regional business are based a key competitive advantage of credit suisse is our ability to bring all the resources of the bank together for our clients – combining our key strengths in private banking with our leading capabilities in equities fixed income corporate finance and asset management across boundaries and divisions we deliver a compelling proposition for clients looking to access a full spectrum of our best products and capabilities to help them expand their businesses as well as protect and grow their wealth our private banking relationship managers not only have trusted client relationships but can also present the full value proposition of our integrated bank bringing the full breadth and depth of knowledge of the bank to our clients  francesco de ferrari head of private banking asia pacific credit suisse  working with you to achieve your wealth goals  relationship get to know credit suisse singapore solutions learn how we partner with our clients research find out more about credit suisse research digital private banking app  at credit suisse we are investing in technology to help us serve our clients even better we are proud to announce the launch of the credit suisse private banking asia pacific app which will empower you aroundtheclock with greater access to relevant information and insights…  learn more for enquiries contact our customer care center at     our customer care center is available from monday am to saturday pm singapore time alternatively send us a message among the most renowned private banks in the world at credit suisse we have been building private banking partnerships for more than  years by drawing on the global presence of our integrated bank we aim to offer you our clients a comprehensive suite of solutions products and advisory services  relationship managers included in the ne